\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {3}{\ignorespaces Comparison of traditional end-to-end approach (top) vs.\ Geo-SLM hybrid neuro-symbolic approach (bottom). Geo-SLM uses geometric measurement for precision and SLM reasoning for semantic understanding.}}{9}{}%
